{"tid":1038543,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"[新手 士多啤梨 食評] 菊池，古都華，櫻花","createTime":"2019-02-26T17:43:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-28T10:00:57.000Z","uid":41315,"like":5,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"1fae7e1b9721da9dc76ae2d4b959a732548c97b5","tid":1038543,"uid":41315,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-26T17:43:48.000Z","msg":"是咁的<br />\n今日生果聚會<br />\n買左堆生果同朋友 share <br />\n順手打個簡評<br />\n<br />\n利申垃圾脷<br />\n唔好屌得咁盡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Mk9qkBP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMk9qkBP.jpg&h=70aef0e9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n日本 奈良縣產 古都華 士多啤梨<br />\n小粒對稱，香甜豐層次，口感甜美<br />\n香味濃郁，有桃&amp;青蘋果既酸甜交集感覺<br />\n層次豐富<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jwsCV6s.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjwsCV6s.jpg&h=1b536e78&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n日本 德島縣產 佐那河櫻花 士多啤梨<br />\n色澤紅潤，對稱均勻，香味清淡<br />\n甜度算中上，但香氣維持續性不足，略為失色<br />\n*無圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n日本 熊本縣產 菊池 士多啤梨<br />\n士多啤梨界重量級王者，沒有之一<br />\n特殊方法以蜜糖培植<br />\n體型巨大，香氣四溢<br />\n飽滿多汁，口感鬆軟<br />\n甜度雖然比不上古都華<br />\n但其特殊香甜氣味持續澎湃奔放<br />\n入口時強烈感受到其香氣<br />\n並於吞嚥後長時間持續<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/auxb0yd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fauxb0yd.jpg&h=a91b9414&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n*圖中為細粒版 菊池<br />\n大粒版 600幾蚊，無買<br />\n<br />\n--------<br />\n同場加映<br />\n<br />\n墨西哥 黑莓(Blackberry)<br />\n香味甜美濃郁多汁<br />\n<br />\n墨西哥 藍莓(Blueberry)<br />\n香氣特殊，帶有香草味道<br />\n酸度低，甜度稍高於智利藍莓<br />\n<br />\n智利 藍莓(Blueberry)<br />\n香甜略帶酸味，質感軟熟<br />\n<br />\n荷蘭 紅醋栗(Red Currant)<br />\n*買唔靚，不作評論<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/r377yTs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fr377yTs.jpg&h=82d1eb9e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2ef71836e916d767ddc85721b43e3c0ff9db0bb3","tid":1038543,"uid":75904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-27T13:36:56.000Z","msg":"甜皇，又平又甜，有香氣"},{"pid":"e2dc80e54a391da99743aee32489dc6187a38056","tid":1038543,"uid":93046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-27T16:04:54.000Z","msg":"邊度買架？"},{"pid":"fdcfb96f2b5a7317bc7ea8806aa3d1626e8d37a0","tid":1038543,"uid":66099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-27T16:24:06.000Z","msg":"rich<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"124f2f312f6a11689a51d12d8326e01ad8bb54ea","tid":1038543,"uid":37204,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"e2dc80e54a391da99743aee32489dc6187a38056","tid":1038543,"uid":93046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-27T16:04:54.000Z","msg":"邊度買架？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T01:54:53.000Z","msg":"royal黎, 你買唔到架"},{"pid":"b39f213fcafcc7677847571cc033f02c31d2dcb5","tid":1038543,"uid":37204,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T01:55:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>邊度買架？</blockquote>royal<span style=\"color: red;\">級</span>黎, 你買唔到架</blockquote>"},{"pid":"1b5c8396213aeb23b915538272a99b75a85c0d83","tid":1038543,"uid":41315,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"124f2f312f6a11689a51d12d8326e01ad8bb54ea","tid":1038543,"uid":37204,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"e2dc80e54a391da99743aee32489dc6187a38056","tid":1038543,"uid":93046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-27T16:04:54.000Z","msg":"邊度買架？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T01:54:53.000Z","msg":"royal黎, 你買唔到架"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T02:13:17.000Z","msg":"係，買唔到<br />\n要去樓下個果柵買<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/fac